*xv-3.10a-r5 (07 Aug 2003)

  04 Sep 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> xv-3.10a-r2.ebuild,
  xv-3.10a-r3.ebuild, xv-3.10a-r4.ebuild, xv-3.10a-r5.ebuild:
  Deleted trailing white-spaces.  Removed unused IUSE flags from -r5.
  Merged ccc support from -r3 to -r5 and removed broken -r4.

  14 Aug 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> xv-3.10a-r5.ebuild,
  files/xv-3.10a-r5-ppc.patch:
  Corrected ppc patch.  Thanks to Christophe Boyanique
  <gentoo@raceme.org>.  Closing bug #26192

  07 Aug 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> xv-3.10a-r5.ebuild,
  files/xv-3.10a-r5-gentoo-Nu.patch:
  Fixed install destination directories.  Thanks to Brandon Anderson
  <branders@ccsoft.com> for bug report #25678.

